Package: pairedmcnemar
Type: Package
Title: Pairwise McNemar Tests vs a Control with Effect Sizes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Peter", family = "Ho", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "YOUR_EMAIL@example.com")
)
Description: Convenience functions to compare a control condition to two or more
    treatments for paired binary outcomes using McNemar tests from the
    contingencytables package, with multiple-testing adjustment and Cohen's g
    effect sizes (with confidence intervals).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    stats,
    contingencytables,
    effectsize
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/PHUoL/pairedmcnemar
BugReports: https://github.com/PHUoL/pairedmcnemar/issues
